window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Charles has returned to a land devastated by war with the wraiths.</p> <p>Alone in a desolate land, seeking his friends and allies, he faces one peril after another.</p> <p>But finding his allies is only the beginning of the journey.</p> <p>A wraith queen has invaded Kortall, her legions wiping all life from the land. Worse, she's awoken ancient magics which will allow her to bring an even greater flood of wraiths across the dimensional barrier.</p> <p>If she's not stopped before the Gate of Worlds is opened, it'll be the end of all life. Nothing will survive the destruction the life-sucking wraiths will inflict.</p> <p>Friends. Magic. Science. Charles will need to blend all he's learned and use every skill and asset available to him, if he's to defeat the Queen once and for all!</p>"; 
